@api_reference
@authentication
API supports authentication via OAuth2 API keys
-Use OAuth2 user-facing applications
-Use API keys server-to-server communication
:rate_limit=1000/m
@authorization
Authorization handled via role-based access control (RBAC)
:_col=permission
:admin=Full access user=Read only service=API access
